tourBios.carHigh:
2014: Played in 11 PGA Tour of Australasia events, a T6 his best showing. Opened and closed with a pair of 71s and then combined those with a second-round 65 and a third-round 68 to T6 at the Western Australia Open in October…Added a T29 at the Indonesian Masters on the Asian Tour in late-April.  
2013: Split his time between the Asian Tour and the PGA Tour of Australasia. Best finish on the Australasia Tour was a T22 at the South Pacific Open in New Caledonia…Top Asian Tour outing was a T19 at the Solaire Open in April.  
2012: Played primarily on the PGA Tour of Australasia, with a couple of appearances on the Asian Tour and five PGA TOUR Canada tournaments. Best performance of the season was a T5 in Canada, at the Times Colonist Island Savings Open. Shot rounds of 72-69-65-67 in June, tying with Scott Harrington, six shots behind winner Andrew Roque…In Australasia, his best showings were a T17 at the Victorian PGA Championship and a T26 at the New South Wales PGA Championship.  
2011: Played in seven combined PGA Tour of Australasia and Asian Tour events, missing the cut in all of them. 
2010: Made three combined starts on the PGA Tour of Australasia and the Japan Golf Tour.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T5th in 2012 at the Times Colonist Island Savings Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 75th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the PGA TOUR Canada.
